{"id":383,"date":"2024-08-02T17:06:09","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T17:06:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=383"},"modified":"2024-08-02T17:06:38","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T17:06:38","slug":"tm003-water-pulse","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm003-water-pulse\/","title":{"rendered":"TM003 Water Pulse"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM003 Water Pulse<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Inside Valley Cave, North of the giant stone tablet and the Gentleman Thomas NPC.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>An attack with a pulsing blast of water. It may also confuse the enemy.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>20<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Water<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Defeat Vega at the Crater Town Gym<\/li>\n<li>Get the <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm01-cut\/\">HM for Cut<\/a> to access Valley Cave<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Starting from outside of the Crater Town Pok\u00e9mon Center, head North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-crater-town-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Crater Town Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Crater Town Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go to the very center of the Crater Town crater and enter Valley Cave. Use Cut to access the cave\u2019s entrance if you haven\u2019t been in before.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-valley-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Entering Valley Cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering Valley Cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Head West inside of the cave and then take the ladder to go down.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-ladder-to-go-deeper-inside-of-the-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the ladder to go deeper inside of the cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the ladder to go deeper inside of the cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Follow the cave South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-following-the-cave-south.jpg\" alt=\"Following the cave South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the cave South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually have to cross two blue and white bridges. These indicate you\u2019re on the right path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-crossing-2-bridges-to-continue-going-south.jpg\" alt=\"Crossing two bridges to continue going South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Crossing two bridges to continue going South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Turn right directly after crossing the second bridge and follow this narrow path hugging the cave\u2019s wall to reach the TM for Water Pulse on the ground.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-tm-for-water-pulse.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the TM for Water Pulse. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the TM for Water Pulse.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":384,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[8],"class_list":["post-383","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tms-hms"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/383","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/139"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/384"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=383"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=383"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}